Scn fbmwMSMatchMakerScript

short MatchMakeFons
short MatchMakeGoval
short MatchMakeSunel
short MatchMakeSwitch
short MatchMakerTimer
short Timerday
short Daysgoneby
short MatchMakeFonsStart
short MatchMakeGovalStart
short MatchMakeSunelStart
short Fate

;####MatchMakerTimer####


begin gamemode

	if MatchMakerTimer == 1
		if ( GetStage fbmwMSMatchMaker == 118 )
			set MatchMakerTimer to 0
		endif

		if ( Daysgoneby == 0 )
			set Timerday to GameDay
			set Daysgoneby to 1
		endif

		if ( Timerday != GameDay )
;presumably it went up...
			set Daysgoneby to Daysgoneby + 1
			set Timerday to GameDay
		endif

		if ( Player.GetInWorldspace WChildMournholdVSGodsreach == 0 )
			if ( Daysgoneby > 2 )
				if ( MatchMakeSwitch == 0 )
					set MatchMakeSwitch to 1
					fbmwMarenaGilnithREF.PositionWorld 620.13,-1160.73,284.33,189.1, WChildMournholdVSGodsreach
					if ( GetStage fbmwMSMatchMaker == 110 )
						Set MatchMakeGovalStart to 1
					elseif ( GetStage fbmwMSMatchMaker == 100 )
						Set MatchMakeSunelStart to 1
					else 
						Set MatchMakeFonsStart to 1
					endif
				endif
			endif
		endif

		if ( Daysgoneby > 3)
			if ( MatchMakeSwitch == 2 )
				SetStage fbmwMSMatchMaker 118
				set MatchMakeSwitch to 3
				fbmwMarenaGilnithREF.PositionWorld -3328.02,280.33,85.97,0, WChildMournholdVSGreatSBazaar
				return
			endif
		endif
	endif

;####MatchMakeFons####

if MatchMakeFonsStart == 1

	If ( MatchMakeSwitch == 4 )
		Set MatchMakeFonsStart to 0
	endif

;if he's dead, make sure this doesn't continue

	if ( GetDeadCount 0FonsSBeren > 0 )
		Set MatchMakeFonsStart to 0
	endif




	If ( MatchMakeSwitch == 1 )
		fbmwFonsBerenREF.PositionWorld 700.13,-1140.73,284.33,131.8 WChildMournholdVSGodsreach
		set MatchMakeSwitch to 2
	endif

	if (MatchMakeSwitch == 3)
		fbmwFonsBerenREF.PositionWorld 2958.76,581.12,336.79,50 WChildMournholdVSGreatSBazaar
		if ( MatchMakeFons == 6 )
			if ( GetRandomPercent > 33 )
				set MatchMakeFons to 7
			else
				set MatchMakeFons to 8
			endif
		endif
		if ( MatchMakeFons == 5 )
			if ( GetRandomPercent > 85 )
				set MatchMakeFons to 7
			else
				set MatchMakeFons to 8
			endif
		endif
		if ( MatchMakeFons == 4 )
			if ( GetRandomPercent > 50 )
				set MatchMakeFons to 7
			else
				set MatchMakeFons to 8
			endif
		endif
		set MatchMakeSwitch to 4
	endif
Endif

;####MatchMakeSunel####

If MatchMakeSunelStart == 1
